These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, alhambra, chaman, game
4 different games are played: go, bridge, scrabble, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indian, turkish, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, bus, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, snowboarding, tennis
 1. the brazilian is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 9. the turkish is the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the indian##1
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar          | alhambra    | chaman      | montecristo  | game     |
| Game         | monopoly    | scrabble   | go | bridge      |
| Nationality   | indian       | brazilian | turkish     | egyptian    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | car         | snowmobile  | bus    |
| Sport           | snowboarding      | tennis       | handball | volleyball |

