.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, electrician, nurse, designer
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, hiking, photography, fishing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, april, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, amber, black
City: san-francisco, venice, berlin, paris
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 4. the designer is on the far right##1
 5. the pilot is on the right of the electrician##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the nurse##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person who likes azure is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
11. the nurse is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | electrician      | pilot     | nurse    | designer |
| Hobby   | camping | hiking   | photography   | fishing           |
| Birthday   | july  | december     | april    | june         |
| Color           | black         | azure | amber     | chestnut        |
| City         | san-francisco     | paris  | venice | berlin       |

