.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, country, house, punk
House: cape-cod, colonial, futuristic, cottage
City: venice, rome, hamburg, miami
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, bridge, monopoly
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, puzzles, collecting
 1. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the fan of house is the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of house##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the cottage house is the person traveling to rome##1
10. the colonial house is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the fan of house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Music-Genre          | d&b    | punk      | house  | country   |
| House   | cottage     | futuristic      | colonial | cape-cod      |
| City           | rome       | venice         | miami  | hamburg         |
| Game         | whist | backgammon | bridge  | monopoly |
| Hobby     | puzzles       | skydiving         | collecting   | card-games        |

