City: marseilles, miami, boston, london
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, pink, orange, light-blue
4 different games are played: chess, monopoly, mah-jongg, go
There 4 different types of food: radish, strawberry, kiwi, lemon
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who likes white##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the colombian is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 5. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the colombian is the person eating strawberry##1
10. the canadian is the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
12. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Nationality    | colombian     | dutch  | canadian       | american      |
| City       | boston    | london        | marseilles  | miami      |
| Color         | pink  | light-blue | white | orange |
| Game         | chess | go          | monopoly         | mah-jongg      |
| Food   | strawberry     | radish     | kiwi       | lemon          |

