.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, bongani, fonseca
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, classical, rock, electronic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, october, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, sailing, badminton, surfing
House: cottage, wooden, colonial, palace
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
 2. the cain-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the fan of rock is the bongani-smoker##1
 6. the fan of electronic is the fonseca-smoker##1
 7. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the palace house##1
 9. the wooden house is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
12. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Cigar      | fonseca       | bongani      | cain      | aristoff    |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | rock | classical | pop  |
| Birthday   | october    | april     | november      | august |
| Sport   | badminton  | surfing     | golf    | sailing  |
| House           | wooden  | palace       | cottage          | colonial      |

