.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, russian, dutch
City: berlin, miami, hannover, hamburg
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, ebony, aquamarine
House: palace, futuristic, modern, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, scientist, electrician, journalist
 1. the modern house is on the far left##1
 2. the dutch is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the electrician is the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the journalist##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the coach##1
 7. the journalist is on the left of the japanese##1
 8. the victorian house is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the canadian##1
10. the victorian house is the russian##1
11. the palace house is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality          | dutch      | canadian     | japanese        | russian     |
| City         | hannover     | berlin    | hamburg | miami |
| Color   | ivory | ebony  | emerald      | aquamarine       |
| House         | modern      | palace | futuristic     | victorian        |
| Job     | electrician   | journalist     | coach  | scientist       |

