.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, zinnia, dahlia
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, blood-red, pink
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, d&b, electronic, disco
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, palace, wooden
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, climbing, snowboarding, biathlon
 1. the fan of disco is the person who likes purple##1
 2. the palace house is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of house##1
 5. the palace house is the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 8. the fan of house is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is the wooden house##1
11. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Flower        | begonia    | dahlia        | aconite        | zinnia      |
| Color       | blood-red       | purple       | emerald      | pink |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | disco | electronic | house      |
| House         | cape-cod          | wooden         | ranch-style           | palace    |
| Sport   | snowboarding         | climbing       | biathlon     | tennis   |

 